channel.title: CVE Feed for Jenkins project -- Jenkins MongoDB Plugin
channel.description: The latest CVEs for Jenkins project -- Jenkins MongoDB Plugin

item.title: CVE-2020-2268|2024-08-04T07:01:41.176Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20mongodb%20plugin
item.description: A cross-site request forgery (CSRF) vulnerability in Jenkins MongoDB Plugin 1.3 and earlier allows attackers to gain access to some metadata of any arbitrary files on the Jenkins controller.

item.title: CVE-2020-2267|2024-08-04T07:01:41.201Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20mongodb%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins MongoDB Plugin 1.3 and earlier allows attackers with Overall/Read permission to gain access to some metadata of any arbitrary files on the Jenkins controller.
